Afef Jnifen (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 3 n'ọnwa Nọvemba n'afọ 1963) bụ onye Tunisia amụrụ n'Ịtali, onye na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-egosi telivishọn.
A mụrụ Jnifen na afo 1963 na Ben Gardane, Tunisia ma bụrụ nwa amaala Ịtali
Ọ bụ nwa nwanyị nke onye bụbu onye nnọchi anya Tunisia bụ Mohamed Jnifen, onye bụkwa onye nnọchi anya na: Libya, Egypt, Saudi Arabia, Lebanon, Syria, Yemen, na Bahrain
Nne ya, Saida Benina, bụ onye Turkish. Ọ lụrụ Marco Tronchetti Provera, onye ọchụnta ego Ịtali, onye isi oche na onye isi ọrụ nke Pirelli & C
Ọrụ ngosi uwe ya malitere mgbe onye na-ese foto bụ Jean-Paul Goude chọpụtara ya, onye hụrụ ya ka ọ na-eje ije n'ụsọ osimiri mgbe ya na Carla Bruni na-agba mgbasa ozi "Club Med" na Bahamas
Goude tinyere Jnifen na mgbasa ozi ahụ ma nye ya aro ka ọ gaa Paris ma zute onye na-emepụta Azzedine Alaïa

Ọ ghọrọ ngwa ngwa ihe nlereanya kachasị amasị ọtụtụ n'ime ndị na-emepụta ihe na Europe, na-eme njem n'etiti Milan na Paris mgbe ọ na-arụ ọrụ maka Armani, Fendi, Jean Paul Gaultier, Roberto Cavalli, na ndị ọzọ. Ọrụ Jnifen na-aga nke ọma na ejiji agafeela afọ iri atọ na-anọchite anya ụdị mba ụwa kachasị elu dịka L'Oréal, Paris.
Na mgbakwunye na ịme ihe ngosi, Afef bụkwa onye na-eme ihe nkiri na-aga nke ọma, nke a maara maka usoro TV La grande notte na afo 2003 na Rai 2
A kwadoro ya na mmemme telivishọn dịka Maurizio Costanzo Show na 1982 na Canale 5 na Quelli che..
il calcio na afo 1993 na Rai 3
Ọ bụkwa onye na-eme ihe ngosi telivishọn na-ewu ewu n'Ịtali, na-akwado, na 1999 ya na Fabrizio Frizzi, Scommettiamo che...
na Rai 1, na, na afo 2006 ya na Gene Gnocchi, La grande notte na Rai 2

N'afọ 2016 na afo 2017, Jnifen pụtara na Project Runway Middle East na MBC dị ka onye otu ndị ọka ikpe ya na onye na-emepụta Lebanon bụ Elie Saab na onye Ijipt na-eme ihe nkiri Yousra. N'afọ 2017, a kpọrọ ya onye nnọchi anya "Fashion 4 Development".
